      "width": 320,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "**dotnet build -c Release**\n.NET 8, references Pro SDK dlls"
    },
    {
      "id": "nodeC2000000001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "**PackageAddIn target**\nto `.esriAddinX` (zip)\n`Config.daml` + `Install/*.dll`"
    },
    {
      "id": "nodeC3000000001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 820,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "**Documents\\ArcGIS\\AddIns\\ArcGISPro**\nPro scans this folder at startup"
    },
    {
      "id": "nodeC4000000001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1240,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 110,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "**Pro startup -> Module1.Initialize()**\nto BridgeServer.Start()  *(listens on :5005)*"
    }
